      <scopecontent id="aspace_e09dfb50efb43f6076a25e31f0359a4c">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records include lecture materials, notes, handouts, and assignments for courses in art history, composition, and painting taught by Richard A. Rathbone, professor of drawing and painting in the Yale Department of Painting.</p>  
